high_descs: Go left to stand in front of the plant and racket on the ground.
Pick the racket up from the ground.
Turn around and go to stand facing the desk with the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a racket in hand.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room.
Pick up the tennis racket that is sitting to the right of the plant on the floor
Turn around and cross the room then hang right and walk to the desk in front of you
Turn on the lamp that is sitting on the desk
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket by the light of a lamp

high_descs: turn left, walk forward past the bed, to the corner
pick up the tennis racket that is on the floor in the corner
turn around, walk back across the room to the other side, turn right, walk forward towards the desk, face the desk
turn the lamp on, hold tennis racket in front of lamp
anns.task_desc: get a tennis racket from the floor to examine it with a lamp

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the tennis racquet on the floor, leaning on the wall
Pick up the tennis racquet from the floor
Turn around and walk to your right until you are at the desk, to the left of the chair
anns.task_desc: Pick up a tennis racquet and then turn on the desk lamp
